responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "87F524184A462BC7B3421A9197370BC4", "If you\'re interested in more work, I\'ve got a spare mare I could part with to assist you. We don\'t need the materials raw, but we could use them after processing. Process the plants, wood and stone you brought back, and I can trade you an old swayback. She\'s not fast, but she\'s faster than you. She\'ll get you down to the refining workstations just fine.")
